{"tid":302051,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[伸手黨］一條友獨遊首爾兩日","createTime":"2017-06-29T05:45:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T10:17:35.000Z","uid":21341,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a2c767c7095d5889cedad32ce4a14296c14fe16","tid":302051,"uid":21341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T05:45:42.000Z","msg":"話說早排買到平機票 同個FD快閃首爾兩日<br />\n點知佢突然有啲急事去唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家我返我一枝公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n坐uo614 聽日出發  uo615星期一返<br />\n<br />\nCheck過首爾果兩日都會有雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身行程諗住到時一齊plan  宜家得返我又唔知點好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無巴絲可以推薦下啲景點 同 可以一條友食飯嘅地方比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   無限感激！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d26e6a2b255c8eda680ca02480da10bbcdede3e","tid":302051,"uid":21122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T05:47:34.000Z","msg":"弘大coffe shop 坐一日"},{"pid":"8a4ea0d9eddfd8d0756495bda1984ac41e752b54","tid":302051,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T05:49:28.000Z","msg":"清溪川鳩行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f79f9cffdcf42cdf82e4c21eac995059d40475a7","tid":302051,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T05:49:50.000Z","msg":"你鍾意睇自然風景，城市，韓妹韓仔，韓流文化定咩野？"},{"pid":"3b75cc4600d70b9c6c3042292fe3376ac7979caf","tid":302051,"uid":21341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T06:04:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你鍾意睇自然風景，城市，韓妹韓仔，韓流文化定咩野？</blockquote><br />\n本來都有諗過去遠啲睇下景  但得兩日好似太chur <br />\n如果無落雨會諗下行山（當然係市區易行果啲）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有睇開綜藝但唔追星<br />\n喺市區好似除左買野 都係買野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"