dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n凌晨3點到首爾咁你做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw其實都幾好,唔洗請假就去到旅行"},{"pid":"793b85951b0021a6de0856a88578866f2a38cd73","tid":302051,"uid":21341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T06:34:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>首爾林公園有鹿餵<br />\n側邊有個貨櫃玻璃屋<br />\n距離好近<br />\n可以休閒咁過成日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89d0bad496c24c5536ec337849b654b30759589a","tid":302051,"uid":21341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T06:36:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>兩日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實樓主係去4日3夜,2日係講full day咁既意思掛</blockquote><br />\n係真係兩日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 星期六03:00到 <br />\n星期一0400走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n凌晨3點到首爾咁你做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw其實都幾好,唔洗請假就去到旅行</blockquote><br />\n係 份工無咩假 請假又要搵人頂好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過應該攰到癲<br />\n去到諗住訓機場或者出首爾站汗蒸幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237ddfbcd280c57e27a928c241397e8e7c3ea4ff","tid":302051,"uid":65234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T06:58:00.000Z","msg":"2日就咪去啦 <br />\nBtw機票幾錢"},{"pid":"6fd98bdc4a277bf11bf1f366f428c502b3050442","tid":302051,"uid":65234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T07:00:05.000Z","msg":"可以去漢江hea 有好大草地 有人busking 好多情侶會去訓草地<br />\n夜晚有夜市 幾好feel"},{"pid":"6a7af3df66